column16: Justin Morneau flies out to right fielder Brennan Boesch.    Ben Revere to 3rd.
Josh Willingham reaches on fielding error by shortstop Ramon Santiago.    Ben Revere to 2nd.
Joe Mauer strikes out on foul tip.
Denard Span grounds out, shortstop Ramon Santiago to first baseman Prince Fielder.
Alexi Casilla flies out to center fielder Austin Jackson.
Brian Dozier called out on strikes.
Trevor Plouffe homers (19) on a fly ball to left field.   Justin Morneau scores.
Chris Heisey singles on a ground ball to third baseman Miguel Cabrera.    Todd Frazier to 3rd.
Zack Cozart pops out to second baseman Danny Worth.
Todd Frazier doubles (8) on a sharp line drive to left fielder Delmon Young.    Miguel Cairo scores.
